trans-unit.source: Provides specifications for protocols and data formats for the messages used in the action supported by the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder spesifikasjoner for protokoller og datoformater for meldinger som er brukt i handling som støttes av XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The `OperationBinding` class corresponds to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) `<operation>` element enclosed by the `<binding>` element, which in turn corresponds to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding> class.
trans-unit.target: Den `OperationBinding` til Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) samsvarer med klassen `<operation>` elementet omsluttet av den `<binding>` elementet som i sin tur tilsvarer <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding>

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om WSDL, kan du se spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Binding"></xref> of which the current <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref> is a member.
The current <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding> is a member of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding.Operations%2A> collection.
A binding of which the current <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref> is a member.
Gets the collection of extensibility elements specific to the current <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter samling av extensibility elementer spesifikke for gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om Web Services (WSDL = Description Language), kan du se spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An `OperationBinding` will be associated with exactly one `InputBinding`.
trans-unit.target: En `OperationBinding` vil være knyttet til nøyaktig én `InputBinding`.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An `OperationBinding` will be associated with exactly one `OutputBinding`.
trans-unit.target: En `OperationBinding` vil være knyttet til nøyaktig én `OutputBinding`.
